snippet.title: v5.5 "Equinox Gate" Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd is ascending to v5.5 "Equinox Gate"!
New S-rank soul-awakened battlesuit Palatinus Equinox and S-rank battlesuit Spina Astera debut!
A Post-Honkai Odyssey Chapter 2 update, featured event Secret Project: Arahato α,
Spring Lobby 2022, and more content coming your way! Stay tuned!
